episodes.title: Bhutte Bane Popcorn
episodes.description: It’s first day for Class 11 commerce students at KLPD. BBFs Anirban and Raman have their very first fight as Anirban decides to change his section to be with her all-time crush, topper Stuti. Meanwhile, Stuti is sad as principal announces that this year’s headgirl and headboy will be only from science section.

episodes.title: Stuti Ko Kaise Pataun?
episodes.description: Dreams come true for Anirban as Stuti chooses to sit next to him. In a hilarious act, Raman interviews candidates to replace Anirban from the position of his best friend. On the other hand, Stuti is shocked when she gets to know that her best friend Kudrat has been chosen as the perfect head girl.

episodes.title: Kisne Mara Atom Bomb?
episodes.description: Raman comes up with a 3-rule strategy to help Anirban impress Stuti, but Dimple doesn’t agree. Stuti is facing a difficult choice, and finally she. makes a radical decision to save her Head Girl dream.

episodes.title: POV: CCTV
episodes.description: Stuti’s decision to switch to Science has left Anirban in great turmoil. Stuti’s crazy plan ‘to have it all’ has Kudrat worried. Stuti pays the price of her bad choices but Anirban manages to save the day for her, and finally the ice is broken.

episodes.title: Masala Mass Bunk
episodes.description: An act of discrimination by Principal Shukla against commerce students pisses Dimple off and she decides to put him in his place, by planning a mass bunk. Stuti is against it, but Dimple lies to her and puts her in a difficult position.

episodes.title: Stuti Ko Kaise Manau?
episodes.description: After the whole bunking mess, Stuti is now ignoring Anirban. Anirban who really want to make things better, try all the things to make her feel better. While Mukund is now after Raman. He has decided to make his life hell.

episodes.title: Mistri Bane Kalakar
episodes.description: Anirban apologizes to Stuti but she is adamant. Mukund gets in a big fight Raman and Dimple. A crazy prank takes place in class, and Raman is wrongly pulled up.

episodes.title: 200 Ka Ek
episodes.description: Stuti forgives Anirban. Raman wants revenge from Mukund. Dimple makes a nasty plan, but at the time of execution, Raman screws up and their BIG plan to avenge their ‘image’ bites them back and how!

episodes.title: Surprise Test Pro Max
episodes.description: The principal drops the surprise test bomb on commerce students. Dimple ends up smuggling Topper Stuti’s notes to earn a quick buck! Mukund uses the ace up his sleeve to deal with the test. Anirban and Stuti are in for a surprise that may put a dent in their newly blossoming friendship.

episodes.title: Stuti Kahan Hai Yaar?
episodes.description: Stuti gives Anirban a serious dressing down, following which, he has a spat with Raman and Dimple. Determined to show students their place, Principal Shukla springs up a Surprise Test 2.0. A bizarre fallout of the test leaves Anirban, Stuti, Raman, Dimple and Mukund accidentally locked inside the store room with no network. The only way for them to get out is by working together as a team.

episodes.title: Who's the hottie?
episodes.description: The first parent-principal meeting doesn’t go well for Mukund. Raman decides to cheer up Mukund, realizing that the big bad bully is actually just a lonely kid. Stuti is missing from the school the next day after the meeting. Commode Raja’s news of her accident shatters Anirban.

episodes.title: Gaurav-Bhagao Andolan
episodes.description: As Cancel Commode Raja’s scoop on Stuti turns out to be fake, Cancel Commode Raja trends in school. Anirban finally musters courage and decides it’s time to tell Stuti how he feels. But hilarity ensues when his hopes are dashed by Mr Perfect – the new brawn with brains boy in school. While Dimple has finally cracked the formula for her start-up.

episodes.title: That's What Friends Do
episodes.description: Anirban and his buddies finally expose the new dazzling and discover what the handsome truth hidden behind his face is.

episodes.title: Dosti Ka Interval
episodes.description: Anirban is furious with Stuti, but Stuti makes every attempt to reestablish his friendship with Anirban, while mobile phones are still banned in school, which has a significant impact on Dimple's life. Finally, Stuti hands over her notes to Anirban, and the two share a moment together.

episodes.title: Analysis-e-Anirban
episodes.description: In this episode, unexpected emotions begin to surface within Stuti as she realizes there is a burgeoning affection for Anirban deep within her heart. Simultaneously, Dimple finds herself contemplating whether she has stumbled upon the love of her life

episodes.title: School Bani Pathshala
episodes.description: The school was thrown into chaos when the principal introduced a new rule segregating boys and girls, creating a deep division among the students. Dimple's heart shattered as she was affected by the consequences of this rule, feeling the pain of separation and loss.

episodes.title: Gender-Bender!
episodes.description: As a bizarre reaction to the canoodling couple, Principal tops the phone ban rule - Girls and boys can’t talk to each other! The school suddenly gives off a black and white era vibe. The only lucky one is Dimple, who can arrange a meet-cute with her crush with no fear of being caught – because her crush is a girl.

episodes.title: Head Girl Kaun Hai?
episodes.description: Dimple confesses her feelings to Harshita. Anirban, Raman and Mukund face the threat of suspension. The whole school turns up in support of them, but in a new avatar. Gender Bender it is! Meanwhile, Principal Shukla’s ad hoc actions are questioned by a well-meaning school board member.

episodes.title: Abey Yeh Kya Ho Gaya?
episodes.description: Anirban wants Stuti to stay back at any cost. But how? With both anger and hormones raging, he executes his amateur plan to get the principal sacked, and have Stuti become the head-girl. Surprisingly, he even succeeds well almost. Just as he’s about to confess his feelings to Stuti, things take an unprecedented turn.

episodes.title: Stuti Roko Andolan
episodes.description: When Anirban musters up the courage to confess his feelings to Stuti, she reveals that she is leaving the school, shocking everyone. Anirban and his friends hatch a plan to convince her to stay. Will they succeed in keeping their friend at school?

episodes.title: Stuti Roko Andolan 2.0
episodes.description: Despite their best efforts, Anirban and his friends fail to convince Stuti. Unyielding, Anirban initiates Plan B. These persistent efforts make Stuti realize how important her friends are to her, and she decides she cannot leave them behind.

episodes.title: RamBan Ka Jhagda?
episodes.description: While everyone is happy for Stuti, Principal Cholla has different plans for her responsibilities. Additionally, Cholla's announcement about new house allotments has left her school friends extremely worried. What are they planning next?

episodes.title: The House Of School Friends
episodes.description: When Gaurav cleverly separates everyone into different houses, Dimples uncovers his ulterior motive. Determined to thwart his plans and reunite her friends, she devises 'The House of School Friends' operation.

episodes.title: Aswachata Abhiyan
episodes.description: School friends plan to get revenge on Principal Cholla by meddling in ACIS visit, forgetting how it might negatively impact Stuti's position as head girl. Despite Anirban's efforts to stop them, it's already too late.

episodes.title: Honest Anirban
episodes.description: Zorawar gets angry seeing litter everywhere and notes it in his diary. Anirban uses paint thrown on a blackboard to create a painting. ACIS inspector Zorawar is impressed by Anirban's art, which covers Raman's mistake.

episodes.title: And The Oscar Goes To
episodes.description: The drawing teacher admires Anirban’s art. The group persuades Raman to audition, and he agrees to participate. However, Raman gets cold feet and disappears, prompting the entire group to search for him.

episodes.title: Stuti Is Punished!
episodes.description: All friends, exhausted from searching for Raman, are surprised when he enters the auditorium in a new avatar. Raman auditions but isn't selected. Dimple despite all the stress manage to celebrate Mukund's birthday.

episodes.title: Golgappa Overflow Ho Gaya!
episodes.description: Gaurav has forced the gang to do his work. Mukund devises a revenge plan against him. As a result, Gaurav is punished, and the gang is now plotting to remove him from his position as head boy.

episodes.title: Head Boy Haye Haye!
episodes.description: The gang learns Gaurav is forging the Principal's signature and devises a plan. Caught on CCTV, Gaurav is demoted from Head Boy. Anirban decides to help Nilesh.

episodes.title: And The Head Boy Is…
episodes.description: Principal appoints Anirban as Head Boy, shocking the gang. Stuti reveals she convinced the principal. Mr. Mehta informs us about the quiz. Stuti, initially upset, changes her mind seeing Principal using the stress bag.

episodes.title: Dimple Ki Toh Lag Gayi
episodes.description: Stuti preps the auditorium for the quiz while Anirban, confused and panicked, is taken to the stress relief corner by her. Raman and others sing to welcome Mr. Zorawar, who starts the quiz with the audience.

episodes.title: Unit Test Ya Picnic?
episodes.description: Students of KLPD face unconventional punishments after a surprise inspection by Mukund's strict mother. With the school at risk, they must choose between a picnic or saving their 11th and 12th grades.

episodes.title: Padhai-Vadhai Sabh Dhokha Hai
episodes.description: Facing pressure from upcoming exams and a retest, students discuss their struggles and strategies. The results bring mixed emotions, and attention shifts to the cultural fest, a crucial factor in the school's evaluation.

episodes.title: Movie Kaun Kaun Dekhega?
episodes.description: To convince their strict principal for movie, students turn a surprise celebration into an appreciation event. However, the movie is a dull documentary, prompting students to sneak out, leading to unexpected twists in relationships.

episodes.title: Haww, Kiss???
episodes.description: After the video emerges, Raman, Mukund, and Dimple confront Anirban and Stuti, triggering chaos. Stuti grapples with the fallout while Anirban tries to repair their friendship amid school tensions and peer judgment.

episodes.title: Clash Of The Genders!
episodes.description: Stuti's rejection of Anirban sparks a dare-filled rivalry between boys and girls. Rising tensions lead to pranks and challenges that strain friendships and reveal underlying emotions.

episodes.title: Rehearsal Time!
episodes.description: In a chaotic library escape, Mukund injures himself, prompting the group to rally around him. This leads to heartwarming moments and a reconciliation between Stuti and Anirban.

episodes.title: Kya Phata Raman!
episodes.description: In the school auditorium, cultural performance rehearsals create tension when Raman is excluded. Ananda Ma'am pairs Kudrat with Gaurav, but Raman's return in high-heeled shoes surprises everyone. Tables turn when he injures his ankle.

episodes.title: Stuti, Yeh Tune Kya Kiya?
episodes.description: In the school auditorium, chaos ensues when Ananda Ma'am falls ill during cultural performance preparations. Anirban steps up to create a last-minute background, but backstage revelations of Chola's deceit spark a student rebellion.

episodes.title: New Girl In Class
episodes.description: Stuti and Anirban's almost-love story faces new hurdles, while Principal Bhola's ban on extracurricular activities stirs up tension. In the midst of canteen laughter, they cross paths with a new girl, Yashika.

episodes.title: Mission: Who Is Yashika?
episodes.description: A new student, Yashika, joins the school, quickly catching Anirban's attention as he begins to show genuine care for her. Stuti, noticing Anirban's growing interest in Yashika, starts to feel a pang of jealousy. As these emotions surface, tension brews between Stuti and Anirban, complicating their friendship.

episodes.title: KLPD Mein Junk Food Ban
episodes.description: Principal Cholla implements a strict ban on junk food in the school canteen, replacing it with healthier options in an effort to promote student well-being. However, not everyone is on board with the new rules. Raman and his group of friends, unhappy with the change, secretly smuggle in junk food, distributing it among the students.

episodes.title: Business Girl Dimple Rocks!
episodes.description: Chaos erupts in the school as several students begin vomiting, seemingly due to food poisoning. Concerned and determined to find the culprit, Dimple takes it upon herself to investigate the canteen's ingredients, suspecting foul play. Her suspicions quickly fall on Raju, and she sets out to trap him, believing he's responsible for the incident.

episodes.title: Kebab Mein Haddi?
episodes.description: Students in class were asked to do a marketing survey in pairs, Since Yashika is a new student, she was given the previlege to chose her partner first, she picked Anirban. Stuti was seen being jealous of this. Then Mukund chose Dimple, which left Stuti with no choice but Raman. They all head to Agarwal sweets for survey where Stuti and Anirban are seated next each other.

episodes.title: And The Best Jodi Is...?
episodes.description: Students had a presentation after the market survey wherein Yashika was seen having panic attacks. She was feeling uneasy, Anirban noticed it and tried to console her by holding her hands. She eventually started feeling better. Stuti was sitting with Raman, she noticed them holding hands which made her feel jealous.

episodes.title: Fight For Seat!
episodes.description: Cholla punishes the students and replaces the benches with mattresses. The students jump over it and have fun, Stuti sees it and tries to stop everyone, Anirban is dragged away by Yashita, Stuti goes and sits next to gaurav. Anirban gets jealous. Students eventually are fed up of the mattresses. The canteen guy offers students to sit on a chair in exchange of money.

episodes.title: Tables Have Turned
episodes.description: Gaurav enters, everyone is furious. Everyone warns him not to tell Cholla, he replies that he himself is frustrated with his dad. Anirban says that they cannot trust him, Stuti takes Gaurav's side. Anirban is now jealous. Gaurav helps in cutting the wire. The power has been cut not only in Cholla's cabin but the whole school. Everyone blames Gaurav, Stuti takes his side and speaks on his behalf.

episodes.title: Walk Of Shame
episodes.description: Everyone tries to find Dimple, that's when they come across scrabble competition, Stuti and Yashika decide to team up for it. Cholla punishes Raman and Mukund. Stuti gets on stage for preparation, Anirban wishes luck to her. Yashika gets panic attacks seeing the stage, Anirban tries to comfort her, Stuti sees it and is jealous.

episodes.title: May The Best Girl Win
episodes.description: Anirban finds the owl gifted to Stuti on floor. Raman and Mukund finally reach Dimple in the hospital. They all chill together. Stuti and Yashika win the 1st round. Gaurav and his partner win too. Now it is Stuti vs Yashika and Gaurav vs his partner. Gaurav makes it look like his partner is cheating, Principal bans all extra curricular activites.

episodes.title: No More Masti In KLPD!
episodes.description: Stuti tries to convince Cholla to remove the ban but he ignores her request. Anirban comes on stage and blames Gaurav for falsely accusing his partner, Stuti interferes and asks Anirban to stay out of their fight. Everyone leaves Anirban alone on stage, except Yashika, she thanks Anirban for being there for her. She is shown admiring Anirban. Everyone gathers and welcomes Dimple.

episodes.title: Matter Ab Serious Hai
episodes.description: Principal walks out of his office and observes furious students protecting by performing a street play, Cholla is still not convinced. Dimple warns Cholla if he doesnt lift the ban, Yashika would post the street play video online and everyone would blame Cholla. He then says that due to this, student's marks would be deducted. Stuti pleads him not to deduct marks.

episodes.title: Commode Raja's Face Revealed
episodes.description: Raman and Mukund's antics have finally exhausted the principal's patience, leading him to humiliate them by making them do a chicken dance in front of the entire school. Dimple, determined to expose the prankster Commode Raja.

episodes.title: School Friends Ka Plan Backfired
episodes.description: Thinking they've caught Commode Raja, the students ambush a figure in a hoodie only to find it's Principal Cholla, sick and annoyed. Just then, Commode Raja sends a taunting message, prompting the group to try a seance.

episodes.title: Mission Red Flag To Green Flag
episodes.description: Anirban tries to impress Stuti, frustrated by her misunderstandings, and sets out to prove he's a "green flag." However, his attempts, including praising Yashika as a "whole green forest," only make Stuti jealous and push her further away.

episodes.title: Sitare vs Bechare
episodes.description: Dimple reveals Principal Cholla's truth to the trustee, exposing how Cholla had restricted extracurricular activities due to their seniors' poor performance. Cholla, in turn, proposes a competition where extracurriculars will be allowed for the winning team. The students are divided into two teams: those who scored above 70 and those below.

episodes.title: My School Friends
episodes.description: After much turmoil, Stuti and Anirban finally reconcile, putting their differences aside and coming together as a team. Determined to set things right, they decide to approach Principal Cholla and convince him to lift the ban that has been troubling everyone. Just as their plan begins to take shape, an unexpected twist shakes things up.

episodes.title: Episode 20
episodes.description: Episode 20 of School Friends

episodes.title: The Honeymoon
episodes.description: Fleeing a media scandal surrounding Irani Pharma, Adhir and Zoya escape for their honeymoon, accompanied by their photographer, Ambika. But their retreat takes a strange turn with the arrival of a mysterious stranger, culminating in a body washing up on the beach.

episodes.title: Suspect No. 1
episodes.description: After Adhir's mysterious death, his powerful parents suspect foul play and bring in relentless cop Divya Sawant to investigate. As she delves into the case, dark secrets emerge, positioning Ambika as the prime suspect in a growing web of lies and conspiracy.

episodes.title: Nowhere to Hide
episodes.description: On the run with nowhere to hide, Ambika unexpectedly finds an ally in Elvin. Together, they begin to unravel the dark secrets that Zoya and the Iranis are desperately concealing. But the closer they get to the truth, the more dangerous their path becomes.

episodes.title: Secrets Tumble Out
episodes.description: Ambika faces the enigmatic stranger from her honeymoon once more, threatening to reveal a secret that could save her. They forge a reluctant alliance to uncover critical evidence and uncover the truth.

episodes.title: On the Run
episodes.description: With the cops closing in, Ambika's bid to clear her name using the evidence backfires, thrusting her into a high-stakes scramble for an unexpected and perilous solution.

episodes.title: Case Closed
episodes.description: In the season finale, Ambika executes her daring final plan to clear her name. As the dust settles, true colors emerge, revealing that no one is safe!

episodes.title: The Puzzle
episodes.description: When Sagar the Chief Editor of ‘Samacharam’ newspaper, finds a crossword puzzle in a dhaba. The puzzle predicts a terrifying incident that would occur in his life.

episodes.title: Editorial Cartoon
episodes.description: Police Detective Kranthi Shenoy is given the suicide case of a popular journalist. While investigating she suspects foul play. Ajay Ghosh under Sagar’s instruction, interrogates Koti which leads to more problems.

episodes.title: Horoscope
episodes.description: Suicide investigation leads Kranthi to gun smuggling racket which eventually leads to the disappearance of Koti. Koti’s truck being involved in the accident, brings Sagar and Ajay Ghosh into the investigation’s purview. During the launch of ‘Samacharam’s’ first copy, Sagar receives a mysterious message in the form of old newspaper scrap.

episodes.title: Crime Report
episodes.description: While Sagar and Ajay Ghosh discuss recent events, they find a clue from the old newspaper scrap which drives their investigation further. Kranti and Ranga discover a connection between the case and Sagar’s farm house. The suspense continues to build.

episodes.title: Page 3
episodes.description: As Kranthi and Ranga continue the investigations they find an unexpected dead body. Sagar follows Kiran Reddy, the research head and host for the YouTube show "Ghost Shadows," and learns about Ravi’s research into journalist’s suicide. Sagar gets a newspaper scrap with yet another ominous prediction.

episodes.title: This Day, That Year
episodes.description: As Kranthi’s investigative net tightens around Sagar, he decides to visit Dhootha Publications in an attempt to unravel the mystery behind Sathyamurthy’s book. The story delves into a shocking past. With this information Sagar goes to the light house, closing in on the truth.

episodes.title: Continued on Page 6
episodes.description: As deaths continue, Sagar is forewarned about an impending danger to his family, he comes clean to Kranthi and together they race against time to stop the newspapers’ deadly prediction.

episodes.title: Headlines
episodes.description: Priya becomes the target of a mysterious killer. As the events unfold, Sagar’s past and family secrets comes to light, Kranti begins to connect the dots to uncover the truth.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Episode 5 of Dhootha

episodes.title: Maine Dekhi Hai Uski Mrityu
episodes.description: Juhi, Rhea's Hindi literature professor, suspects her of cheating in her term essay and fails her. Later, Rhea manipulates Arun, the hostel security guard, to get Juhi’s address.

episodes.title: Nishaane Pe Sirf Main Thi
episodes.description: Juhi and Neil’s relationship begins to fall through the cracks. Juhi and Rhea's rivalry becomes public after she deliberately humiliates Rhea in class. Rhea visits Juhi's house and meets Neil.

episodes.title: Sach Ke Kai Pehlu
episodes.description: Juhi becomes increasingly suspicious about Rhea after she loses her wedding ring. She notices Rhea wearing her wedding ring and attacks her at the founder's day party. Neil and Juhi have a huge fight.

episodes.title: Sach Ki Tarah Log Bhi Complex Hote Hain
episodes.description: Juhi goes through emotional turmoil and seeks support from her parents. Anand pays a visit to Rhea. Rhea seduces Neil while Juhi is at her parents' anniversary party.

episodes.title: Hum Sab Mein Ek Cheat Hota Hai
episodes.description: Neil shows Juhi the picture he found in his pocket. Juhi confronts Anand about the picture and he confesses the truth about Rhea. Rhea reveals her past to Neil. Juhi returns home to a shocking sight.

episodes.title: Tum Phool Si, Main Kaante Si
episodes.description: Sunanda is convinced that there is more to the story and digs deeper into Rhea's life. Anand manages to get Rhea to confess her crime. Rhea attempts to reach out to Juhi, but her hopes are shattered.

episodes.title: Chehre Pe Chehra
episodes.description: Juhi is accused of plagiarism by Amit Chaudhary. She suspects Rhea to be behind the allegation. Meanwhile, Rhea’s plan to inherit the Rajguru estate is at risk. A shocking revelation awaits Anand.

episodes.title: We Are Family
episodes.description: Amit serves a legal notice to Juhi through Anand. Anand’s attempt to meet Amit and resolve the matter only complicates it further. On the other hand, Rhea learns about Juhi’s past with Vishal.

episodes.title: The Darkest Hour
episodes.description: Juhi learns about Anand’s confession of plagiarising from Amit and publicly takes the blame to protect Anand. A guilt-ridden Anand apologizes to Juhi and Rhea before taking a drastic step.

episodes.title: I Will Never Stop
episodes.description: Juhi tries to find the truth behind the plagiarism allegations. Meanwhile, Rhea searches for Yash's real father. When Yash goes missing, Juhi suspects Rhea and takes the police to the Rajguru estate.

episodes.title: Jo Karna Tha, Mujhe Karna Tha
episodes.description: Arun's obsession endangers Yash, forcing Rhea and Amit to fight him. Juhi gets admitted to a mental facility after hearing of Yash's death. Amit becomes fearful of Rhea's ambitions.

episodes.title: Tum Aur Main Alag Nahi
episodes.description: Amit tells Juhi that Yash is alive and with Rhea. Juhi tricks Rhea to continue her search for Yash at the Rajguru estate. A final confrontation with Rhea forces Juhi to turn the tables.

episodes.title: Sins of the Past
episodes.description: Reyna Malik's first day back at work after a year-long hiatus. She is ready to take on the world. But will the dark forces let her?

episodes.title: I See You
episodes.description: Are Reyna's medicines causing her to hallucinate? Or is she being haunted by some evil?

episodes.title: Lonely Nightmares
episodes.description: Reyna meets Sahil, her new neighbor. A breath of fresh air in her life!

episodes.title: Friendly Betrayal
episodes.description: Shekhar brings a psychic to Reyna's house. The psychic does notice something distressing, but he stops himself from coming to Reyna's help.

episodes.title: Evil Everywhere
episodes.description: Sahil helps Reyna and her friend connect with the force that is haunting her. But this leads them to a dark twist.

episodes.title: Dusk to Dawn
episodes.description: Reyna is in an emotionally fragile state as Meghna dies in a freak accident. Reyna finds it difficult to be with Shekhar anymore. Sahil and Reyna share a night of passion.

episodes.title: At Last an Angel
episodes.description: Reyna is in a mess because nothing is as it seems. She can no longer trust herself - will she get help from the beyond?

episodes.title: Roots of Evil
episodes.description: Reyna is in a mess because nothing is as it seems. She can no longer trust herself - will she get help from the beyond?

episodes.title: One More Try
episodes.description: The moment of truth is here. Everyone has gathered to protect Reyna from the evil. United, will they be able to fight the spirit off?

episodes.title: The Last Battle
episodes.description: In this final episode Reyna fights unto death to overcome the evil. But Roshni is required to make a huge sacrifice.

episodes.title: Know Thyself
episodes.description: A rebel jumps the wall as a new girl enters campus. Old friends huddle with their gang in hopes of winning the secret shed and with it, the right to rule the Vandana Valley campus.

episodes.title: Ready to Fight
episodes.description: A new drama teacher holds auditions for the annual play as love brews on campus. An important basketball game could seal the fate of two hearts.

episodes.title: Love Lies
episodes.description: A campus divides and loyalties are tested when a scandal erupts. Temperatures soar further when boys visit for the hotly anticipated Socials dance.

episodes.title: Phir bhi udd gaye
episodes.description: Midterms, baby! Secrets are spilled and characters are tested when the girls head into nature for their class camping trip. A mysterious stranger cooks up a feast.

episodes.title: Masoom nahin hoon mein
episodes.description: Tension mounts as the whole campus prepares for the 75th Annual Day event. Hearts break over opportunities missed, and new resolutions are formed.

episodes.title: The Perfect Woman
episodes.description: Everyone puts their best foot forward as the school’s Diamond jubilee celebrations unfold. The illusion of perfection is challenged as truths are discovered and a long lost friend returns.

episodes.title: Together We Win
episodes.description: The term comes to an end as our girls are tested in more ways than one. A protest erupts as our girls struggle to define which truths are worth fighting for.

episodes.title: Mallikajaan: The Queen of Heeramandi
episodes.description: As Mallikajaan reigns over her courtesans, rebellion grows on the streets. Alamzeb has her first brush with love. Wali shares key information with Bibbo.

episodes.title: Fareedanjaan: The Challenger Returns
episodes.description: Heartbroken by a nawab, Lajjo turns to drink and dance to win back her former lover. Mallikajaan reveals a dark secret as her past catches up with her.

episodes.title: Waheedajaan - Scarred for Life
episodes.description: The return of Fareedan to Khwabgah raises tensions as Mallikajaan schemes to cling onto her control. Waheedan makes a bold move of her own.

episodes.title: Alamzeb: The Innocent Pawn
episodes.description: As her dance debut approaches, Alam questions her place at Heeramandi. Saima unwittingly earns Mallikajaan's ire and Fareedan strikes back.

episodes.title: Tajdar: The Lover’s Dilemma
episodes.description: As Mallikajaan and the courtesans fervently search for Alam, Tajdar comes to her rescue. Meanwhile, an enraged Waheedan has a proposal for Fareedan.

episodes.title: Tajdar & Alamzeb: Nation vs. Love
episodes.description: Alam and Tajdar’s romance intensifies as a rebellion is being hatched. Mallikajaan and Fareedan uncover dark and disturbing secrets about each other.

episodes.title: Bibbojaan - Long Live the Revolution
episodes.description: Cartwright’s scheme against the courtesans unfolds. Seeking a future with Alam, Tajdar approaches Mallikajaan — but her approval comes at a price.

episodes.title: Heeramandi: The Swan Song
episodes.description: The fight for freedom reaches the steps of Heeramandi — for both the courtesans and the country. Will the battle end in victory or result in ruination?

episodes.title: Episode 1
episodes.description: Swathi's illicit affair takes a shocking turn. Dreaming of opening a hotel, Prabhakar looks to his brother Arvind for support.

episodes.title: Episode 2
episodes.description: A determined Thupalli digs into the case of a newly discovered dead body. Umesh and Swathi take desperate measures to cover their tracks.

episodes.title: Episode 3
episodes.description: After learning that Prabhakar was blackmailed, an irate Arvind digs into Umesh's past. Inspector Hassan wades into Thupalli's case findings.

episodes.title: Episode 4
episodes.description: The police question Swathi and Umesh, while a new blackmailer emerges. Hassan's hallucinations spark questions and new leads.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Appu and Swathi form an alliance, but a suspicious Lucas intervenes. Arvind has a plan of his own. An explosive showdown leaves a bloody mess.

episodes.title: Episode 6
episodes.description: At the hospital, tensions run high as secrets threaten to emerge. Hassan makes a startling discovery that changes the course of the case.

episodes.title: Episode 7
episodes.description: Appu takes matters into her own hands, while the police investigate Mehrunisa's connection to Manisha Koirala. Kirtima delivers an ultimatum.

episodes.title: Episode 8
episodes.description: Hassan attempts to crack the case one last time. As the grand opening for Swathi's restaurant approaches, she finally finds her soup's secret ingredient.

episodes.title: Bhookha Shehar
episodes.description: The lives of two estranged friends, Jende, a cop, and Peter, a journalist, turn upside down with the murder of a gay sex worker at the Mahim toilet. This leads them to embark on a thrilling journey exploring the 'hungry' yet 'deadly' city of Mumbai.

episodes.title: Hisaab Barabar
episodes.description: As the murder of another victim sends shock waves around town, life brings Jende face-to-face with Peter, as he is suspicious of Sunil's being involved in the crime. To add to this, Sunil has also been missing for a few days.

episodes.title: Baap Bada Ya Beta
episodes.description: A serial killer is on the loose, and the next target is the cop itself. While stress levels rise at work, Jende's conflict with his father intensifies, distancing him from his other family members. Peter reaches out to an old friend.

episodes.title: Do Se Dosti
episodes.description: Sunil comes back and proves his innocence to Jende. As Peter and Jende's world collide, old wounds are reopened, and differences are resolved. By letting bygones be bygones, their friendship is rekindled. But a vicious future lies ahead for both.

episodes.title: Pappu Ka Bhoot
episodes.description: As the shadow of doom falls on the police itself, two cops from Jende's team meet a fateful end. As the pressure mounts on Jende, he starts suspecting Peter's involvement in the murders. Peter starts challenging his notions about the LGBTQ community.

episodes.title: Honey trapping
episodes.description: As Jende and Peter get a whiff of the 'honey trapping' racket run by the police, the chase to find the culprit gets even tougher. While Rabbani's reality is revealed to her family, Peter and Jende are also hit hard by a truth bomb.

episodes.title: Jhootha Sach
episodes.description: Peter's conflict with Sunil intensifies as he demands to know more about his personal life. Rabbani is jolted by the news of the suicide of her partner. Peter and Jende find the culprit behind these murders, but he escapes in the nick of time.

episodes.title: Barabari Ki Baari
episodes.description: The police up their ante to find the criminal on the run. Peter supports his son, and Jende stands up for Rabbani against the indiscriminate acts of his superior. Peter and Jende solve the case to find themselves on the cusp of another 'beginning'.

episodes.title: Intro
episodes.description: Ankit Pandey enters hostel to ﬁnd that the room allotted to him is already occupied by Chirag and Jaat. He has to ﬁnd himself a room, and a bed that too in the ragging period.

episodes.title: Proving Identity
episodes.description: Ankit grapples with identity crisis as he ﬁnds himself pretty ordinary amongst his batch-mates.

episodes.title: F.O.S.L.A
episodes.description: Ankit is smitten by Akanksha, the most prized catch of not only his batch but entire college. Will a coy Ankit succeed?

episodes.title: GPL
episodes.description: Ankit tries to hide his birthday from his wing-mates to avoid the dreaded GPL. Will he succeed?

episodes.title: End Sem
episodes.description: With Chirag suddenly gone unavailable at the last moment, Ankit and Jhantoo have to survive the end-sems.

episodes.title: D.I.S.C.O
episodes.description: The gang is a year older and realises their authoritative role as seniors not realising that “breaking ice” with the juniors could land them into trouble.

episodes.title: Love-Square
episodes.description: We have all been through love triangles. But when Jaat and Jhantoo end up falling for the same girl a love square is formed. With Ankit and Chirag as catalysts, both pursue Unnati, the heartthrob of the hostel.

episodes.title: Gandagi
episodes.description: Ankit does everything in his power to woo Akanksha by showing her how clean he is in a typical dirty boys hostel. Akanksha however doesn’t seem impressed leaving Ankit heartbroken.

episodes.title: Ghar Wapsi
episodes.description: The gang is all prepared to leave for their homes during the break except for Jhantoo who must stay back. Through the course of the days the boys discover if home is the place to stay or hostel, the place to be.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Episode 5 of Hostel Daze

episodes.title: Failed Experiments
episodes.description: In order to make their lives exciting in third year, the group put themselves through a series of experiments.

episodes.title: Wing Chor
episodes.description: Chirag turns detective to find a notorious thief in the hostel, meanwhile someone spills Akanksha’s secrets to her mother.

episodes.title: Lights Camera Cut
episodes.description: The team led by Chirag, gears up to make a short film in order to win the inter-hostel competition.

episodes.title: Dosti Ka Udhar
episodes.description: The group gets divided as a dispute ensues between two friends messing up their friendship.

episodes.title: G.S.H.A
episodes.description: Jhantoo contests election against a worthy opponent for the post of General Secretary of Hostel Affairs.

episodes.title: Dear Seniors
episodes.description: As the year ends, the group prepares to bid a final goodbye to their seniors, also introspecting their own relationships.

episodes.title: Single Room
episodes.description: As the seniors are allotted single rooms in the hostel, the gang refuses to get serious about their final year until reality hits them in the form of an unexpected event.

episodes.title: Curriculum Vitae
episodes.description: Ankit struggles to write his CV while Chirag and Nabomita have a difficult time keeping their relationship a secret.

episodes.title: Compromise
episodes.description: Jhantu tries to focus on his placements preparation but ends up getting involved in a hostel fight

episodes.title: Day Zero
episodes.description: Day Zero of placement is here and its a testing time for the group.

episodes.title: The Offer
episodes.description: Tensions rise high as the placement season is in it’s full swing and the gang must give it all to leave the hostel with a job in hand.

episodes.title: Hostel Departure
episodes.description: It's the end of a journey where everyone gets to say their final goodbyes to their beloved hostel. But each person does it in their own way.

episodes.title: Boom!
episodes.description: Tired of their abusive husbands, three women plan and execute their murders. It is an almost perfect plan, till Pankaj Mishra - assigned to the case -- realises there is more to it than met the eye.

episodes.title: Freedom, Life, and Choices
episodes.description: The three widows try to get their lives back on track, but they face various unexpected situations that keep them on their toes. Unbeknownst to them, a different and sinister plot is unfolding at the lake house, and Rameez seems to be aware of it.

episodes.title: Teddy Bear
episodes.description: Inspector Pankaj is certain that he is on to something when he tries to trace the explosives used in the blast. Jatin tries to make sense of the attempt on his life, connecting it to his closely guarded secrets. The mysterious plot around MediPharma thickens even as the women, completely unaware of it, try to make sense of the turns their lives are taking.

episodes.title: The Killer
episodes.description: Kavita's desire to find a connection with someone will take her down a strange path. Jatin needs to get his hands on a key piece of evidence before it is too late. Convinced that there is more to the cases, Pankaj and Rinku continue with their investigation, making Inaaya and Barry uncomfortable. Jayati and Veera try to crack a business deal with Inaaya Thakur but are unaware of her dangerous intentions.

episodes.title: No More A Victim
episodes.description: While Kavita is obsessed with her 'true love' and her blog, both Jayati and Veera realise just how precarious their future could be. Jayati forms a bond with Jahaan while Veera is rescued from her misery by a friend. Meanwhile, Jatin struggles to find a solution to his problem, and Pankaj and Rinku inch closer to discovering the complete truth. Where will it lead them?

episodes.title: The Deal
episodes.description: Veera faces a harsh reality that splits her path from that of her friends. Meanwhile, Jayati's determination to break Inaaya meets with an unexpected obstacle. Kavita's involvement with Jahaan leads to dire consequences. Pankaj and Rinku continue to dig further as new layers to the case are exposed. Inaaya comes up with a plan to cover her tracks but, a long shot by Jatin could ruin it all.

episodes.title: Purple Moments
episodes.description: Jatin tries to expose Inaaya, but his attempt hits a roadblock. Veera and Jayati must play their cards smartly with Inaaya, or they risk losing more than they are aware of. Veera finds it difficult to hold on to her hatred for Jatin and tries to balance her feelings between him and Eddie. Meanwhile, Rinku feels jealous about Pankaj's diverted attention.

episodes.title: Jatin Must Die
episodes.description: Veera can barely hold on to her secrets from her friends and Eddie when they all fall in grave danger. The friendship between the three women starts falling apart as they disagree on their next move. Kavita closes an old chapter of her life. While Inaaya's two accomplices pose a threat to each other, Pankaj and Rinku must find proof to support their version of the truth.

episodes.title: Crossroads
episodes.description: Kavita is worried about her future and considers taking a drastic step. Veera decides to help Jatin in his quest while Pankaj and Rinku attempt to unravel a possible conspiracy by connecting the dots. Jayati and Inaaya lock horns, but a jealous Kavita might change the game. Will the three women go their separate ways?

episodes.title: Flash Drive
episodes.description: While Pankaj deals with the blurring lines between his personal and professional life, Jatin hatches a grand plan to solve a problem. Veera must make a tough choice while Pankaj confronts Jayati. Unlikely allies come up with a way to end Inaaya's threat. Meanwhile, Kavita finds herself at the losing end yet again. Will she pose a threat?

episodes.title: Love and Death
episodes.description: Kavita's situation threatens to put the entire plot in danger while Rinku's rage pushes her to a point of no return. All lines converge, and every action bears a consequence. What does fate have in store for Kavita, Veera and Jayati?

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Episode 5 of Black Widows

episodes.title: Egregious
episodes.description: Tyagi seeks key support in his campaign for bar president. Harvard grad Anaya Shroff struggles to find her footing… and a desk.

episodes.title: Dignity
episodes.description: When a monkey causes a stir on the court premises, the lawyers are moved to strike, leading to a strain on Ananya and her first case.

episodes.title: Aukaat
episodes.description: Sujata tries to drop her “foyer lawyer” status with a new client — a foul-mouthed parrot. When a big-shot lawyer arrives, Tyagi and Bagai hatch a plan.

episodes.title: Touch
episodes.description: Ananya and Sujata scramble to help an inmate fulfill her dream to start a family. Tyagi has an emotional talk with his father, a retired judge.

episodes.title: Biradari
episodes.description: Tyagi and his campaign land in hot water after police and lawyers clash. Ananya and Sujata contend with a fierce woman in the race.

episodes.title: Kutai
episodes.description: Phorey or Tyagi? The election results are finally in — but the twists aren't over yet. Ananya turns counselor for a young woman’s case.

episodes.title: Law vs Justice
episodes.description: Tyagi weighs an important decision that will change the course of his career. PP Sahab and Ananya are pulled into a landmark case.

episodes.title: Karm
episodes.description: Karma Talwar's entry into the elite Alibaug circle disturbs high-society queen Indrani Kothari. It soon becomes clear that Karma has a dark past. She is on a mission and has her first target in sight.

episodes.title: Bharosa
episodes.description: Karma begins wooing Ahaan Kothari, so Indrani puts her security head Sameer after her. As Karma plots the downfall of her second target, she meets Vedant, her childhood friend.

episodes.title: Annyaay
episodes.description: Karma's next target is the man who convicted her dad. Indrani's suspicions increase when Ahaan and Karma meet his ex-girlfriend. Meanwhile, his friend Krish makes an entry.

episodes.title: Andhere Raaz
episodes.description: Next, Karma trains her sights on Indrani's trusted psychic healer, who left a deep wound in her as a child. Krish becomes a stumbling block to Ahaan and Karma's relationship.

episodes.title: Hisaab Barabar
episodes.description: Ahaan and Karma finally confront each other. Kaushal panics when Dolly threatens him. Moreover, she finds an interesting photograph in her apartment.

episodes.title: Dil Aur Dimaag
episodes.description: Kaushal is aghast to watch Dolly's video. Krish tells Ahaan about his parent's equation. Deeply shaken, Ahaan joins Bombil Cafe where Vedant becomes his taskmaster.

episodes.title: Vaada
episodes.description: Sameer uncovers a darker secret about Karma's past. While she is living the high life in Alibaug with Ahaan, unbeknownst to her, Ambika Mehra's revenge plan may be at risk.

episodes.title: Super Sidey
episodes.description: On the first day of 9th standard, Samvidhan Sharma, the eternal sidekick finally gets a chance to speak to his crush and the school’s prettiest girl Jasmine. But things take a turn for the worse, when Jasmine’s best friend and sidekick Aadhya, accuses him of cheating.

episodes.title: Crime And Punishment
episodes.description: After a complaint to their strict school principal, Samvidhan and Prateek are not allowed to perform their rap on the Founder’s Day of Lucknow Central Convent school. Samvidhan assumes that Aadhya has made the complaint and has a huge showdown with her. But this misunderstanding leads to an unexpected friendship. Could this be the start of a new romance between the two sidekicks?

episodes.title: Bulati Hai Magar...
episodes.description: Aadhya and Sam form an organic connection and discover they have a lot in common. The once-enemies now talk all day on their phones and through hidden messages left in their favourite book in the school library for each other. When they team up for a flying model competition, their chemistry only gets stronger. But does Aadhya have the same feelings about Sam, or is he just another friend?

episodes.title: Maa Ki Aankh
episodes.description: Sam realises that he is in love for the first time and decides to propose to her. As Aadhya's strict mother Vandita joins school as a substitute teacher, bad timing and luck continue to be his fatal foes. As a worried Aadhya distances herself from Sam, and misunderstandings follow, Sam becomes anxious about Aadhya's blossoming friendship with Sahil, the most popular senior and aspiring poet.

episodes.title: Mera Pehla Pehla Valentine Hai
episodes.description: Students and teachers alike, including Sam and Aadhya, are prepping for their Valentine's Day dates at Lucknow Central Convent. However, Aadhya's father's sudden visit on February 14th throws Sam and Aadhya's preparations into chaos. Will Aadhya be able to make it to Sam's romantic night packed of surprises, or will another surprise catch them off guard and them to question their relationship?

episodes.title: Final Exam
episodes.description: When Sahil, the most popular senior in school, becomes a huge bone of contention between Sam and Aadhya, Sam decides to break up with Aadhya, leaving her completely shocked and confused. All this right in the middle of their final exams. Will Sam ever be able to get over his insecurities and stop comparing his sidekick self to Sahil or will he let go of his first love?

episodes.title: Sam Kahan Hai?
episodes.description: As the school reopens after summer vacations, Aadhya is confronted with some harsh realities, and Sahil is appointed as the leader of the delegation to represent LCC at Celesta Interschool Cultural Festival that is to be hosted by current champions and archrivals Francis Convent School. While Aadhya tries to cope and deal with the shock, something is brewing to heal her. But will that be enough?

episodes.title: Naam Wahi, Dosti Nayi
episodes.description: In their first interaction, Aadhya declines the help offered by Samarth. On the other hand, while Prateek's and Zoya's differences come out into the open as Sahil begins auditioning for Celesta, Jaz finds an opportunity to get closer to Sahil. As the team brainstorms on the topic for Triveni, the main event of Celesta, Aadhya recognises a friend in Samarth.

episodes.title: Emotions Ki Wrong Delivery
episodes.description: While Sahil struggles to assert control over his indisciplined team and finds a friend in Jaz who motivates him, Aadhya faces embarrassment at school due to a personal message getting leaked, which she blames Samarth for. Feeling dejected by him, she finds a friend in her mother who helps her understand things in context while Samarth gets into his first school fight.

episodes.title: Chemistry
episodes.description: Aadhya reaches out and mends things with Samarth. Sahil gets a hint of how Jaz feels about him and Prateek learns his lesson as Jaz and Zoya indulge in a catfight as they audition for debate team on the topic of love. While Prateek and Zoya patch up and Aadhya and Sahil engage in a bitter argument, Father Lawrence announces a mandatory test for all team members to retain their place in the team.

episodes.title: Time Time Ki Baat Hai
episodes.description: As the practise sessions extend beyond school hours, Zoya encourages Jaz to express her feelings for Sahil. Samarth makes Aadhya sneak out of school and surprises her only to be surprised himself. The LCC team suffers a last minute setback as they lose a topic to Francis Convent due to late submission.

episodes.title: Winners and Losers
episodes.description: Team LCC manages to find a topic after a last-minute setback but finds itself on slippery ground as the cracks within the team widen and they lag behind on the points table.While Sahil finds a way to keep the team united and competitive, Samarth realises the stakes on his shoulders for the team's victory.The competition closes with a surprise as our characters are confronted with revelations.

episodes.title: Azaadi
episodes.description: With the board exams concluding, Father Lawrence offers the students of standards 11 and 12 to use their summer holidays for an exciting summer exchange programme- Young Tarang, at Don Roberts School, Dehradun, which brings a smile to Aadhya's face, and she gets on to the task of persuading Zoya and Jaz, who are unsure about the trip.

episodes.title: Ice Breaker
episodes.description: Aadhya and Samarth reunite after manoeuvring through months of long-distance relationship, and are set to finally spend some quality time with each other as others forge some new associations at summer camp.

episodes.title: Surprise Ya Shock
episodes.description: Samarth tries to plan the best birthday for Aadhya, full of surprises. However, little does he know that while his best efforts seem to fall flat, he'll eventually be left shocked himself.

episodes.title: Saavdhaani Hati Durghatna Ghati
episodes.description: As Samarth tries hard to recover from the shock, his equation with Aadhya continues to go downhill. While Aadhya tries her best to make the most of her time with Samarth by managing to get him inducted as a volunteer in Young Tarang, others in the group also struggle with their insecurities as new associations take over the existing bonds.

episodes.title: Dil Dosti Dooriyan
episodes.description: As the camp enters its final leg, on one hand, Aadhya and Samarth contemplate the future of their relationship, while on the other hand, some friends patch up to set out on a new adventure. However, things get worse when a few misadventures damage LCC's reputation, and they find themselves on the verge of a premature exit from the camp.

episodes.title: Picture Abhi Baaki Hai Mere Dost
episodes.description: The LCC gang survives the storm with some interference from their faculties and manages to conclude the summer camp successfully. However, as they are set to return to Lucknow, while some new friendships come to a sweet end, Aadhya and Samarth meet to discuss the future of their relationship. But little does Aadhya know that just when she feels that her life is driven by her decisions.

episodes.title: The Sound of Metal
episodes.description: A brutal road accident that kills a young man. When the man’s mother, Chandana, tells Meenakshi that it wasn’t an accident and requests her to investigate it, Meenakshi refuses saying PI’s have no business investigating murders. But can she stay away?

episodes.title: The Death Freeze
episodes.description: Still unsure, Meenakshi starts digging. She starts suspecting that the dead man was somehow linked to a mysterious virus outbreak in the village of Littnong, Eastern Himalayas.

episodes.title: The Heart of Darkness
episodes.description: Now convinced that the young man was indeed killed, Meenakshi undertakes a reckless journey to Littnong, seeking to find the killer.

episodes.title: The Pretender's Bluder
episodes.description: Meenakshi starts building her theory around the virus. Soon realises that her own life could be under threat.

episodes.title: The Hidden Hazard
episodes.description: A virus starts breaking out around Kolkata. Meenakshi’s investigation picks up speed. A Central Intelligence officer warns Meenakshi to stay away from something that’s way beyond her comprehension.

episodes.title: The Live Data
episodes.description: Kolkata is gripped by the virus outbreak. Meenakshi links the Kolkata virus to the Littnong one. Unknown to her, games are being played by her own accomplices about the identity of the virus. She must go back to Littnong to find some light.

episodes.title: The Boat Called Ujaan
episodes.description: A few earth-shattering breakthroughs stab Meenakshi’s heart. She decides not to continue with her investigation any more only to be brought back to it by her friend. Because now it is not just a man’s death but the need to stop a genocide.

episodes.title: The Reckless Sister
episodes.description: When Meenakshi finally cracks her case, she needs to act. And act she does. Most recklessly.

episodes.title: Meri Tumhari
episodes.description: Mala Kumari, a top-tier star in the Hindi film industry accuses reputed filmaker Divendu Khurana, of sexually assaulting her. As the court battle uncovers areas that are not all black and white, Kashaf attempts to find justice for Mala while Deepak defends Divendu Khurana in his plea for innocence.

episodes.title: Finisher
episodes.description: A 19-year-old engineering student brutally kills a cab driver. Despite it being an open and shut murder case, Kashaf takes it up and eventually finds the motive behind his act. Shubhangi, LN Khanna's granddaughter, joins Deepak's team against the will of her cousin, Shubhrat. An SMS that would damage the reputation of Kashaf's father, Justice Munawwar Quaze, goes viral.

episodes.title: Paani
episodes.description: Deepak is representing a cola company accused of causing a drought in a village in Maharashtra. Kashaf and Vandana are on the other side. Under pressure from Bhalla, Deepak hires a private investigator to dig deeper into the allegations against Justice Quaze. Deepak and Shubhangi start getting romantically involved. Shubhrat finds a way to damage Deepak's reputation in KKA.

episodes.title: Spermaa
episodes.description: A woman gets fired from a startup company on grounds of misconduct and behavioural issues. She approaches Kashaf and Vandana for legal help. Shubhrat Khanna's girlfriend, Ria Singh, breaks shocking news that damages the Quaze family's reputation. The environment at KKA becomes grim with the ever growing rivalry between Deepak and Shubhrat. Ria and Shubhrat decide to take Deepak down together.

episodes.title: Aalaap
episodes.description: A group of music directors decide to sue a guy who's come up with a music software that samples music from various songs to create a new song. Kashaf holds a press conference to prove her father's innocence. Deepak tries to rekindle old flames with Kashaf while on the music case in Mumbai... Abhijeet notices it all. Ria and Shubhrat make their first move on bringing Deepak down.

episodes.title: Ehno
episodes.description: Deepak hands over her first independent case to Shubhangi. She is to defend a driverless car company that's accused of causing an accident. A bitter Abhijeet opens up a can of worms about Deepak. Kashaf confronts her mother about a past incident that's haunted her. Ria goes to Himachal to dig deeper into the Bhalla case. Shubhangi sees Deepak and Kashaf together and gets upset.

episodes.title: Deep Waters
episodes.description: Deepak's brother-in-law seeks his help about a case which involves a Private Security Agent killing himself. Deepak takes the case to Kashaf and Vandana while LN Khanna and Shubhangi defend the private security company in an MP court. Bhalla warns Deepak to shut Ria Singh's investigation down. Shubhrat finds a 'nail in the coffin' moment to end Deepak's career in KKA.

episodes.title: Plan Your Baby
episodes.description: A couple accuses an IVF clinic of giving them a damaged embryo, resulting in their son being born with a disability. Kashaf manages to confront the demons from her past. Deepak goes back to his village to find out more about Bhalla's history. A powerful acquaintance of Bhalla gets involved in the case. Parvathy gives Deepak shocking information about the Quaze case.

episodes.title: Alola
episodes.description: Shubhangi takes up the case of her friends who want to sue a dating app for fraud and cheating. Shubhrat convinces Diraaj and Shamsher to fire Deepak from KKA. Justice Quaze gets a threat letter. He tells Kashaf about it and that Deepak is swimming with sharks in murky waters. She confronts Deepak about it.

episodes.title: Guilt
episodes.description: Kashaf decides to leave the Quaze house after getting some devastating information. Deepak goes to Mumbai in search of his childhood friend who might have more leads about the Bhalla case. Shubhrat calls for a meeting of the partners of KKA to vote Deepak out. Quaze gets another threat, this time with a casualty. A final verdict is given on the Bhalla case and consequences follow.

episodes.title: Tum Mujhpe Bharosa Karti Ho?
episodes.description: Aarya and Tej's family life turns upside down when her brother, Sangram, and their friend, Jawahar, take a dangerous risk to make a quick buck.

episodes.title: Aapko Shaq Hai Kisi Par?
episodes.description: Tragedy strikes home. Adding insult to injury, Aarya has to deal with an unforeseen pressure from the police. In the midst of all this, Aarya begins to suspect someone.

episodes.title: Kaun Zimmedar Hai?
episodes.description: While the family reels in distress, Jawahar warns Aarya about the danger they all are in. When she visits Sangram in the jail, a shock awaits her.

episodes.title: Apne Panje Bahar Nikaalo
episodes.description: Aarya is threatened by an unknown assailant, which ups her worry about her children's safety, who are dealing with their own problems. But she finds an unlikely ally in Daulat.

episodes.title: Kaun Chalaega Business?
episodes.description: Danger strikes Aarya and her family once more, and the relentless Khan searches her house yet again. Fed up, Aarya decides to take the bull by the horns and meets Shekhawat.

episodes.title: Ek Guru Chahiye
episodes.description: As Aarya dives deep into the business, she faces her first challenge. In the meantime, Khan goes after Hina for information, while Jawahar and Daulat get into a scuffle.

episodes.title: Aapki Mummy Don Hai
episodes.description: The worst has happened and Aarya goes looking for Jawahar. Distressed, she informs Shekhawat about a change in plan, only to find him uncaring. How will she keep her kids safe?

episodes.title: Grahan Hai Aaj
episodes.description: Aarya shares with Veer and Aru the challenges she has been facing, and promises to end all the suffering with a master plan. Will everything fall into place?

episodes.title: Dharm Sankat
episodes.description: Despite losing the case, Khan is adamant to find the truth. As another tragedy strikes and the family is in the depths of despair, Aarya is left with a fresh dilemma.

episodes.title: Mujhe Yahaan Se Bhaagna Hai
episodes.description: Forced to return to testify against her family, Aarya is caught in a whirlwind of her bloodied past, the one she has been running away from.

episodes.title: An Eye For An Eye
episodes.description: Aarya drowns in the fear of being attacked by her enemies as she tries to find ways to run away from the country. However, someone is keeping an eye on her.

episodes.title: Ab Hum Vaapis Jaa Rahe Hain
episodes.description: Aarya's past returns to help her in restoring normalcy, and her plans to escape seem to be taking shape. But an unexpected event may create new obstacles.

episodes.title: Sangram Kahaan Hai?
episodes.description: Sangram's disappearance becomes a hurdle to Aarya's plans. Meanwhile, Hina reveals something unpleasant to Aarya.

episodes.title: 300 Crore Ka Consignment
episodes.description: As another tragedy shakes her family, Aarya is shocked to find the Rs 300 crore consignment returned to her life.

episodes.title: I Hate You, Mom
episodes.description: The Sareen family struggles to stay united. In this true test of time, what will Aarya lose next?

episodes.title: Phir Se Panje Baahar Nikaalo
episodes.description: As Hina spirals in her grief, Aarya is pushed to the brink by the Russians and Shekhawat. Will she seek Daulat's help?

episodes.title: Isko Mere Raaste Se Hataa Do
episodes.description: When an unexpected outcome shakes her conscience, Aarya realises she can't run away from her reality. A final confrontation turns her into someone she never thought she would be.

episodes.title: Episode 9
episodes.description: Episode 9 of Aarya

episodes.title: Galti Ki Saza Maut
episodes.description: Aarya faces the impossible choice between protecting her son's love and protecting her family from the Russians. Meanwhile, Sooraj tortures Roop to ensure Aarya's destruction.

episodes.title: Sherni Ka Shikar
episodes.description: Dangerous heroin suppliers Nalini Sahiba and Abhimanyu threaten Aarya if the consignment is not retrieved. As Aarya hunts for Sooraj, she struggles with her sons and Khan.

episodes.title: Bali Ya Balidaan
episodes.description: Sooraj's quest to find Nandini's remains pushes him to extreme lengths. In the meantime, Veer, Maya, Aarya and Sooraj find themselves bound by revenge and regret.

episodes.title: Sherni Ke Shikaar Ka Waqt Aa Gaya Hai
episodes.description: Thanks to the seized consignment, Aarya and Nalini Sahiba end up in the crosshairs of Mikhail, the new Russian boss. Betrayals come to light, and a crucial meeting turns bloody.

episodes.title: Khabri Ki Sazaa Maut
episodes.description: Daulat abandons his new life to help Aarya again. Sampat faces Aarya's wrath for shooting Dhruv, but Aru blames her. Nalini Sahiba and Mikhail put Aarya in a tight spot.

episodes.title: Aarya Sareen Is An Unfit Mother
episodes.description: The welfare officer finally meets the whole family. However, an unpleasant interruption becomes disastrous. As business and family collide, how will Aarya protect her loved ones?

episodes.title: Panje Nikalne Ka Waqt Aa Gaya Hai
episodes.description: Having lost everything she holds dear, Aarya takes an inevitable step. Caught between the Russians, Nalini Sahiba and Khan, how will Aarya redeem herself?

episodes.title: Paisa Kamaya Nahin Banaya Jata Hain
episodes.description: A job opportunity brings Abdul Karim Telgi, a fruit seller from Khanpur, to Bombay. When he is arrested for forgery nine years later, he meets Kaushal Jhaveri in prison and joins his gum wash operation. However, fining the business unscalable, Abdul comes up with the idea to pivot into the world of stamp papers.

episodes.title: Choomantar
episodes.description: Abdul successfully begins to steal official stamp papers from trains, but needs a licence to sell them in bulk. Against Kaushal’s wishes, he uses political connections to try and acquire one from the Old Custom House but fails. To make matters worse, Kaushal, feeling betrayed, leaves Abdul’s side.

episodes.title: Khota Sikka
episodes.description: Abdul manages to acquire a license through political contacts but turns his back on the minister that helped him by allying with the new party in power. He ends up losing his license and going back to prison, where he meets a mechanic from Nashik who introduces him to the source of stamp papers - the Nashik Security Press.

episodes.title: Mubarak Ho Aapko Stamp Paper Hua Hain
episodes.description: Abdul formulates a strategy to get the management of the Nashik Press on his side and facilitates the promotion of their top bureaucrat. He gets the original machines, dyes and papers from the press and starts printing stamp papers. Although he expands his business, he soon learns that, to truly flourish, he must wipe out his biggest competitor.

episodes.title: I Love You
episodes.description: By manipulating the shutdown of the press and the supply chain of the Old Custom House, Abdul monopolizes the stamp market. His success having caught the attention of many, Abdul begins to befriend every new and bigger power in the state.

episodes.title: Episode 7
episodes.description: Episode 7 of Scam 2003

episodes.title: The Legend of Lady Rose
episodes.description: When her fiancé is implicated as the prime suspect in a murder, Charulata 'Charlie' Chopra rushes to his family home in Solang Valley to uncover the mysteries around this death and the secrets of this sleepy hill town.

episodes.title: Sansani
episodes.description: After the explosive arrival of Nikki leaves the entire family reeling, Charlie begins to dig into their secrets, aided by a reluctant partnership with Sitaram.

episodes.title: Keh Do Ki Ye Jhooth Hai
episodes.description: When Solang Valley is rocked by a second death in a matter of weeks, Charlie’s investigation kicks into an overdrive, as she reopens questions that others thought were already answered.

episodes.title: Organic Honey
episodes.description: After a personal betrayal, Charlie becomes obsessed with unearthing the truth no matter the cost, but her reckless pursuit gives way to more enemies than answers.

episodes.title: Main Phuddu Aan
episodes.description: Narrowly escaping a close call with death, Charlie reunites with Sitaram. Together they race against time to find the murderer, because now they’re next on the list.

episodes.title: Look Within
episodes.description: More lives are lost, secrets unearthed, and betrayals come to light in the final chapter of Charlie’s investigation.

episodes.title: Upar Neeche
episodes.description: After breaking a tooth while hunting for blood, Rumi crosses paths with Roy, a timid dentist. Kartik, an outcast cop, looks into a mysterious case.

episodes.title: The Cutmundus
episodes.description: Roy's rare blood sparks interest from Rumi's clan, as Sreela is sent after him. Kartik’s case sends a signal to a secret cabal of vampire hunters.

episodes.title: Climate Change
episodes.description: When a vampire is killed, an awakened Ora bans access to the human world above ground. Hell-bent on revenge, Rumi seeks help from an unlikely source.

episodes.title: The Test
episodes.description: Badshah is taken underground. Kartik learns about his father's past from Luna Luka. At a family dinner, Roy grows suspicious over Rumi's true nature.

episodes.title: Darinda
episodes.description: Roy struggles with his feelings for Rumi. The Cutmundus plot to uncover the vampires' secrets, while Rumi ponders grief, love and loss of her past.

episodes.title: Tyajet Kularthe Purusham
episodes.description: The death of a Cutmundus member leads Luna down a vengeful path. Believing that Roy is a vampire, a desperate Kartik resorts to blackmail.

episodes.title: Meet the Parents
episodes.description: Dinner at the Roy's turns into a night of drunken revelry, while Rumi and Roy take an intimate step. Later, Badshah's revelation puts Rumi in danger.

episodes.title: No. 30
episodes.description: Rumi is faced with a devastating ultimatum — go after Luna, or lose Roy forever. A figure from Luna's past returns to her life.

episodes.title: Sleep with the Fishes
episodes.description: Shukla, a power-hungry politician, plots to topple the government. Two luckless strangers find that they have a common enemy and a thirst for revenge.

episodes.title: Enemy of My Enemy
episodes.description: The team takes shape as Ansari and J.P. Yadav join forces with a bumbling cop and a wily con man — and hatch a plot to steal Shukla's ill-gotten cash.

episodes.title: Playing with Fire
episodes.description: A key member of Shukla's inner circle becomes a silent but vengeful ally. Ansari springs into action when a massive fire breaks out at Pathaani Tola.

episodes.title: Secrets Revealed
episodes.description: Shukla schemes to drive a wedge between Ansari and a rageful Baankeylal. Bela is caught in the crossfire when Ansari’s former allies seek revenge.

episodes.title: So It Begins...
episodes.description: An abduction pushes Bela to take matters into her own hands. The gang scrambles after a drunken Baankeylal puts their mission in jeopardy.

episodes.title: Et tu, Brute?
episodes.description: Disguised as an all-knowing seer, Triloki edges closer to Shukla. When Ansari's loyalty is questioned, plans for the heist spiral into crisis.

episodes.title: Caught Before the Act
episodes.description: On the day of the solar eclipse, the theft is set in motion. But unexpected bumps throw the team's carefully laid plans into major turbulence.

episodes.title: The Eclipse
episodes.description: A surprising development propels the plan forward. Will the stars align for these misfits — or will fortune fall in Shukla's favor?

episodes.title: The Second Coming
episodes.description: A shattered Noyonika Sengupta ends her long sabbatical to return to work as a junior lawyer after her famous husband Rajiv Sengupta is jailed in a sex and corruption scandal.

episodes.title: Scenes from a Marriage
episodes.description: Noyonika takes up the case of a friend’s son accused of murder. She faces criticism from Malini at work. When Sharad Jhadav spills Rajiv's old secrets, she confronts him.

episodes.title: Winds of Change
episodes.description: At work, Noyonika faces pressure but finds a friend in Sana. She learns about Rajiv's illegal dealings and gets upset with her mother-in-law for taking her kids to meet him in jail.

episodes.title: Dirty Little Lies
episodes.description: When opposition lawyer, Shivani Bahl drags Noyonika's personal life to court, she needs to publicly disclose some scandalous truths to get justice. How will Noyonika handle it all?

episodes.title: Family Secrets
episodes.description: A high-profile couple comes under the police radar for their maid's death. Trying to save them, Noyonika straddles legal boundaries. Meanwhile, Rajiv gets a chance at freedom.

episodes.title: Lifeline
episodes.description: A case of a soon-to-be mother and her at-risk unborn child takes Noyonika and Vishal out of town. Back home, the girls tell Rajiv about the packages the family has been receiving.

episodes.title: Trial by Media
episodes.description: Noyonika gears up to fight against Daksh Rathod. Ilyas has a suggestion for Rajiv. When Rajiv’s lawyer leaves him high and dry, Noyonika finds a solution.

episodes.title: Cloak & Dagger
episodes.description: Noyonika fights tooth and nail for Rajiv with Vishal's help as she struggles with her feelings for the two men. In the end, Rajiv's decision leaves her feeling betrayed again.

episodes.title: Hush Hush
episodes.description: Noyonika faces a tough choice when a young masseuse accuses a revered public figure of sexual assault, caught between the truth and her husband Rajiv's rising political career.

episodes.title: Social Dilemma
episodes.description: Noyonika defends influencer Shanaya in an attempted murder trial. Just as Shanaya's bail is revoked, Ananya reveals a shocking truth, flipping the case upside down.

episodes.title: Bad Marriages, Bad Parents
episodes.description: While Noyonika's parenting is tested, she's blindsided by a sharp opposing lawyer in a case against a builder. At work, as alliances shift, Malini feels her position is threatened.

episodes.title: Split Them Up
episodes.description: Rajiv's campaign suffers when Narayani gains sympathy. As Malini's offer tests Noyonika's loyalty, the firm defends two lovers in a murder case, where one needs to be sacrificed.

episodes.title: Sins of the Father
episodes.description: Noyonika uncovers a conspiracy behind the builder case. After a shocking raid shakes her family, Noyonika confronts Narayani and makes a bold move that could change everything.

episodes.title: We Always Want What We Can't Have
episodes.description: As Noyonika wins the builder case and Rajiv's campaign soars, a secret from the past destroys their marriage. Betrayed but empowered, she chooses truth, closure and a new beginning.
